text: Mittelbiberach is a municipality in Biberach in Baden-Württemberg in Germany. It is 3 km west of Biberach an der Riß. The mayor of Mittelbiberach is Florian Hänle since 2018. The river Rotbach flows through the municipality. Reute, Oberdorf, Findenmösle, Unterreute and Geradsweiler are parts of Mittelbiberach. In 2022, 4,441 people live in Mittelbiberach. == References == Category:Biberach (district)
